{
  "stem": "1169.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was that special police who were very vicious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some stores that were open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ghetto itself did not last that long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't like ghettos in Poland that lasted an extensive period of time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole ghetto was a few short weeks before deportation time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Hungary, the Germans had already a lot of experience, and they worked very fast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- nobody tried to intervene.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody tried to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hungarians were very anti-Semitic, and they supported this with great love and zest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they deported us on the open trucks, we saw people all around the streets happy, joyful, and smiling.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Hungarians were very glad to come and take over the Jewish apartments.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was absolutely no sympathy or help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we lived in an-- in an open society, and we were very friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went to their birthdays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came to ours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this was very blatant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I imagine the most blatant aspect of this was that these best of friends deserted you in the moment of need.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They just-- they supported the enemy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then you develop the feeling that remains to this day, I imagine, that you don't trust these people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that they were the ones who came one night, about 12 midnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the apartment house had an inner court, U-shaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came and made a big announcement in the middle of the night that everybody has to pack and get ready to leave at 6:00 AM.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
